These are Puzzles for 6x3 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-8-1::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: basketball, snowboarding, surfing
3 different pets are kept: rabbit, frog, dog
House: colonial, ranch-style, palace
The people have 3 different hobbies: video-games, gardening, writing
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: tulip, zinnia, begonia
There are 3 different favourite colors: black, blue, pink
 1. the owner of the frog is somewhere to the right of the owner of the rabbit##5
 2. the person who's hobby is video-games is not to the right of the palace house##8
 3. the person who's sport is surfing is not to the left of the ranch-style house##8
 4. the colonial house is the person who growsbegonia##1
 5. the person who growszinnia is somewhere to the right of the person who likes black##5
 6. the person who likes blue is on the left or right of the person who growstulip##3
 7. the person who's hobby is video-games is somewhere to the right of the person who growsbegonia##5
 8. the person who likes blue is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 9. the owner of the frog is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is surfing##5
10. the person who likes blue is not to the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##8
11. the person who likes pink is on the far left##1
12. the person who's hobby is writing is not to the right of the owner of the frog##8
13. the person who's hobby is writing is somewhere between the palace house and the person who's sport is basketball##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3     |
| Sport          | basketball | snowboarding | surfing    |
| Pet           | rabbit | frog   | dog     |
| House   | colonial     | ranch-style   | palace       |
| Hobby   | gardening    | writing   | video-games     |
| Flower   | begonia    | tulip   | zinnia |
| Color     | pink     | black | blue     |

