 9. the person traveling to boston is not the person who's birthday is in january##6
10. the person who's birthday is in november is somewhere to the right of the person eating spinach##5
11. the person traveling to boston is not to the right of the person traveling to hamburg##8
12. the art-deco house is somewhere to the left of the futuristic house##5
13. the futuristic house is somewhere between the aristoff-smoker and the person eating strawberry##7

