3 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, cain, aristoff
House: wooden, modern, art-deco
 1. the owner of the mouse is not the modern house##6
 2. the owner of the cat is not to the right of the person who likes green##8
 3. the vegafina-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in march##5
 4. the aristoff-smoker is not the art-deco house##6
 5. the person who's birthday is in august is between the person who likes azure and the cain-smoker##2
 6. the wooden house is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in march is not to the left of the person who likes azure##8
 8. the person eating artichoke is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in october and the person who likes azure##7
 9. the person eating pumpkin is not the person who's birthday is in august##6
10. the modern house is between the owner of the mouse and the art-deco house##2
11. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person eating tomato##1
12. the person who likes brown is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |        2        |     3     |
| Birthday      | march       | august         | october      |
| Color         | azure     | brown         | green    |
| Food           | pumpkin  | artichoke | tomato |
| Pet   | mouse    | cat        | fish      |
| Cigar         | aristoff  | vegafina        | cain    |
| House     | wooden | modern      | art-deco      |

